name: Jump System / Climb Track
Pre Lift
Confirm concrete strength MPA 15 has been reached at connection points (Builder to supply)
Signage in place (Stripping in progress/Jumping in progress/ No access)
Exclusion Zone in place
Spotters in place on slab below jump (outside exclusion zone)
All Platforms cleaned and clear from rubbish
All loose materials removed from edge
Clear communication between team leaders and Crane crew (toolbox talk)
Ladders available and secured
Flipper systems lubricated
Trailing Decks clean of debris
Trailing decks clear of protruding ferrals in walls above
Check exclusion zones in pit below are in place
Plumber to check pipes to water cooler
Transfer RL heights
Post Lift
Confirm connection points are secure and all engaged
Confirm mesh secured to doors and penetrations
Signage in place
Screens and mesh infills are in place and secure
Loose materials are stacked and secure each day
Platforms cleaned and clear from rubbish
All loose materials removed from edge
Loads on platforms not exceeded
Ladders available and secured
Access is clear and marked
Power Board connected
Hangers and planks have been secured
Confirm ready for lift with all involved - Team Leaders
